## Path aliases

Always use `@/` — maps to `./src/*` in tsconfig.json.

```ts
// ✓ correct
import { createClient } from "@/lib/supabase/server"
import { ok, fail, withAuth } from "@/lib/api"
import type { Store, Order } from "@/types"

// ✗ wrong — never use ~/ or relative paths across folders
import { createClient } from "../../lib/supabase/server"
```

