## Supabase clients — use the right one

```ts
// 1. SERVER CLIENT — Server Components, API Routes, Server Actions
//    Respects RLS, reads session from cookies
//    MUST be awaited (Next.js 15)
import { createClient } from "@/lib/supabase/server"
const supabase = await createClient()

// 2. BROWSER CLIENT — Client Components only
//    Use for: auth state listeners, realtime subscriptions
import { createClient } from "@/lib/supabase/client"
const supabase = createClient()

// 3. ADMIN CLIENT — Webhooks, cron jobs, server-only operations
//    Bypasses RLS — use with extreme care
//    NEVER import in Client Components
import { createAdminClient } from "@/lib/supabase/admin"
const supabase = createAdminClient()
```

