## Analytics tracking — `src/lib/utils/analytics.ts`

Client-side only, fire-and-forget. Use in storefront pages only.

```ts
import {
  track,               // base function — any event
  trackPageView,       // call in useEffect on every storefront page
  trackProductView,    // on product detail page mount
  trackCartAdd,        // when item added to cart
  trackCheckoutStart,  // when checkout page opens
  trackOrderPlaced,    // after successful order submission
} from "@/lib/utils/analytics"

// Usage in a storefront component:
useEffect(() => {
  trackPageView(store.id)
  trackProductView(store.id, product.id)
}, [store.id, product.id])
```

