| Plan | Price | Max stores | Max products | Features |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| starter | 99 MAD/mo | 1 | 50 | Basic |
| growth | 249 MAD/mo | 1 | unlimited | +analytics, custom domain, WhatsApp |
