## Supabase setup checklist (do this once)

1. Create project at supabase.com
2. Run `database-schema.sql` in SQL Editor (tables + indexes + RLS policies)
3. Run `supabase-triggers.sql` in SQL Editor (profile trigger + decrement_stock + updated_at)
4. Create storage buckets: `store-assets` and `product-images` (both public)
5. Generate types: `npm run db:types`

### DB trigger quick reference
- `on_auth_user_created` — auto-creates `profiles` row on signup
- `on_profile_created` — auto-seeds 30-day `starter` subscription
- `decrement_stock(p_variant_id, p_quantity)` — RPC, prevents race conditions on stock
- `set_updated_at` — auto-updates `updated_at` on all major tables

