## Common mistakes to avoid

| Mistake | Correct approach |
|---|---|
| `const supabase = createClient()` in server code | `const supabase = await createClient()` |
| Accessing `params.id` directly in route handler | `const { id } = await params` |
| Using `useFormState` from react-dom | `useActionState` from react |
| Storing prices as floats (150.00) | Integers in MAD (150) |
| Joining products table for order history | Use snapshot columns on order_items |
| Importing admin client in a Client Component | Admin client is server-only only |
| Skipping `withRateLimit` on public routes | Always wrap public routes |
| Direct `NextResponse.json()` in routes | Always use `ok()` / `fail()` helpers |
| Manual `WHERE user_id = x` in queries | RLS handles it automatically |
| Updating analytics_events rows | Table is append-only, never UPDATE |
